-- =============================================
-- PEDAGOGICAL DESIGN
-- =============================================

-- NULL handling
--   Agents 2 (phone), 3 (email) – missing contact
--   Clients 3 (email), 4 (phone), 6 (email) – missing contact
--   Properties 4, 7 (zip) – missing postal code
--   Viewings 2,5,9 (feedback) – missing feedback

-- Status values
--   Properties: Active (5), Pending (2), Sold (1), Withdrawn (1)
--   Offers: Accepted (4), Pending (3), Rejected (1), Withdrawn (1)
--   Clients: Buyer (4), Seller (2), Both (2)

-- Property types
--   Single-Family (4), Condo (3), Multi-Family (1), Land (1), Commercial (1)

-- Date ranges
--   Viewings: Jan–Mar 2025
--   Offers: Jan–Mar 2025
--   Contracts: Feb–Apr 2025
--   Payments: Jan–Apr 2025

-- Price ranges
--   List prices: 150,000 to 1,200,000
--   Offer amounts: 285,000 to 1,180,000
--   Sale prices: 440,000 to 920,000
--   Payment amounts: 44,000 to 747,000

-- Edge cases
--   Agent 6 (Robert Garcia) has no properties listed → LEFT JOIN detection
--   Client 8 (Olivia Zhang) has no viewings → LEFT JOIN detection
--   Property 7 (404 Cedar Ln) has no offers → LEFT JOIN detection
--   Property 11 (808 Elm St) has no contract → LEFT JOIN detection
--   Contract 4 has only 1 payment (edge case for GROUP BY)
--   Contract 1 and 3 have 3 payments each (for aggregation)

